Sam, your name was passed along to me as someone that maybe able to help us.

We are investigating the prospect of emailing our confirmations vs faxing

them and one of the things that came up was the possibility of a drop box

email address for the counterparty involved that would be setup in the global

counterparty system. Any ideas off the top of your head of what it might take

to get this information included in the global counterparty system?


 -----Original Message-----

From:  Goodwin, Herbert

